Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:03.78,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\pos(575,295)}憂鬱的four trips
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:08.96,NEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途的天空的盡頭的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.78,0:01:28.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれそうな夢の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:33.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}よろこびを探す世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:44.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君はどんな輝きで　明日へと跳ぶの？　教えてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:50.70,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}声になった未来の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}始まりの my melody 聞こえた？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:02:02.36,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm READY！ 空が青く高くて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:07.33,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}涙ぐんだ今を忘れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:13.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひたすら進もうと誓うから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:17.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}分かりあった瞬間は大切な
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:20.36,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop road
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:20.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an7}ずっと一緒に　君と一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:23.63,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていればいいね多分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:26.38,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと一緒だ　君と一緒で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:29.06,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在の鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:35.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you READY？ だから今を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:40.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誇らしくなるね君の想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:46.14,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}やたらに眩しいよその笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:50.39,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向かいあって本心は負けないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:53.96,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.78,0:01:28.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}灑落著夢的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:33.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是找尋著喜悅的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:44.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你帶著怎樣的光芒 向著明日起航 告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:56.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傾聽憧憬著未來的心跳 那是我邁向明天的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:02:02.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm READY! 無垠的天空湛藍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:07.33,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不要忘記今天的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:13.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約定好一起大步向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:17.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心靈相通的瞬間 是如此珍重的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:20.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop road
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:20.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}想要一直在一起 同你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:23.63,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要有微笑就別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:26.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在一起 和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:29.06,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊握通向明天的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:35.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you READY? 所以我相信現在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:40.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的思念讓我自豪無比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:46.14,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的笑臉是那麼的光彩奪目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:50.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直面真心就不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:53.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop mind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:48.23,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}急に黙り込んで　君は手を繋いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:53.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}茜空に消えてく今日を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:58.26,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}見送る長いかげぼうし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:03.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}放課後は永遠みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:07.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}サヨナラをごまかしてたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:18.04,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}だけど心は旅立ちの予感を知ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:24.46,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}果てしない未来への
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.63,0:22:29.12,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}躊躇いを隠して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:37.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}微笑む君の夢が眩しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:43.49,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あと少しの季節を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:48.29,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}惜しむようにはしゃいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:57.38,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明日への帰り道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:48.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}突然沉默不語的你 靜靜地把我的手握起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:53.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}漸漸延向地平線的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:58.26,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}訴說著一天又隨著夕陽沉去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:03.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你說放學後的時光就像永恆一樣漫長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:07.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}把離別的那一刻深藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:18.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}但是彼此卻都深知即將各自啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:29.12,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}掩飾著對未知旅途的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:37.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}微笑著的你 夢想是那樣的絢麗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:43.49,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}讓我們珍惜這所剩無幾的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:48.29,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}盡情歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:57.38,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}然後踏上通往明天的歸程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19\fad(200,0)}（您有一條新消息）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  已經收拾的差不多了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去一趟市政廳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去辦遷戶口的手續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  你今天要和夏海她們去玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不是每天都約好出去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  偶爾也由你主動約她們一次如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}（今天有空嗎？出去玩嗎？）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香會不會又做什麼蠢事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  你現在在家裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香有沒有打電話給你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒  出什麼事了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  是旅遊  大家一起去旅遊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是真正的巴厘島
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從早玩到晚的巴厘島五日游
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去外國？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有護照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  隨心所欲的沖繩三日游
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕坐飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼北海道也不行了咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呢  成吉思汗鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的預算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預支零花錢的話  大概2  3萬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概也就這點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒戲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐電車去不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗星臥鋪特快？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼  電車？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個反而更貴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  紗季你儘是在發牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼到底去哪裏好  紗季想去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？我隨便…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便才是最讓人頭疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去還在計劃階段就泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  京都？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  還有舞女體驗  看上去好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就變成修學旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修學旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  修學旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年不能一起去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想大家一起去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只在那個時候回來一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經是決定好了的事  就不要再多提了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅遊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也決定不了去處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是大家一起去哪裏玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏是指哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去紗季要搬去的地方看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家去親眼見證一下紗季的新家是怎麼樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個人一起的修學旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯  真不錯呢  東京  順便觀光一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴空塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Sky Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去武道館  巨蛋也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是演唱會的會場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你們去了我的新家也不會覺得多有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  不是挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去東京  東京  東京
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是在東京  但其實是個小島
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐船要11個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是要去已經很麻煩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在東京一個叫做竹芝的地方坐船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上出發早上才到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能訂到船票呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫你打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我想預約幾張船票
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的  初中生四名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一股防蟲劑的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不買新的不行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你們要去小島？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候轉學我也覺得很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是個好地方  你一定會喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英語的作業你做好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天輪到我上去講
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不是也會輪到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜你帶字典了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香也沒帶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很重嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣  那該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  老師來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這夢是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛  要不要買呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要試穿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不好意思  稍微等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季不買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  但看了就想買啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  暈車藥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有暈電車和暈船用的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事要馬上聯繫我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小島如果紗季能喜歡上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會下雨嗎  凜子你帶傘了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的包也太小了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都那麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說以防萬一還是輕裝上陣的好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小島上有什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰熊之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說會稍微晚點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香  真沒辦法  我先給你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指南？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  是紗季寫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得一次的旅遊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季從以前開始就很較真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞的像是真的修學旅行一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過虧了某個人的福  一上來行程稍微有點變化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  抱歉  我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  下田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時的離別
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CD放在播放器裏忘拿出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶來想要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓大家一起聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我存進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是凜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:09:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了嗎  我要放了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是去一次九段下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（九段下: 武道館所在地）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有那麼多錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人好多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是濱松町  濱松町  出口在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  船在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  是竹芝棧橋方向…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是東京塔  東京塔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我拍一張
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京塔  和凜一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其實也想多來這種地方看看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啊  我們又不是來觀光的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼想去我的新家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說都會好奇吧  為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  我也是第一次去  可沒法保證那兒會有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  夏海  來拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要喊這麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點  這麼漂亮多拍幾張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你悠閒地拍了那麼多紀念照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  真大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  去外面瞧瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩虹橋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  東京
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有離開東京
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說船會搖得很厲害 但這完全沒有問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似出了東京灣就會搖得厲害了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了暈船藥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 優香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先要把行李安頓好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（免責聲明 本次航程有可能無法到達目的地）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據情況  有可能會到不了那個島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是如果浪太高  船就無法停泊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中途返回？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  我們的位子是最邊上的兩個和旁邊的兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自的票上都寫著號碼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先到先得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜也要邊上的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點 放好行李就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  凜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  像小孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡子裏沒有什麼奇怪的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為還不到午夜零點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說  我不敢上廁所了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你按住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特等席是最好的席位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有很厲害的人物在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去 會被罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…紗季害怕被罵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:14:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香  給你枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜也接著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不換上睡衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都沒換啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只把這個脫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間用不著躲躲藏藏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓周圍的人感到尷尬的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能躺下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了很多無用功呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  夜晚才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是零食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外過夜是一定要吃夜宵的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  你不需要減肥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點  我費了很大勁帶來的  吃啦吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是清湯口味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}給我一片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是特濃口味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 紗季 張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到修學旅行的晚上就想到？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔枕頭大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試膽大會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討論戀愛話題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  紗季竟然說討論戀愛話題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼說  但其實？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼說  但其實？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那夏海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶得太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你們看…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位乘客  馬上就要到熄燈時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在本船正在東京灣內向著三宅島航行中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外由於今天天氣惡劣  海上浪高  預計船會搖得很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:17:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建議容易暈船的乘客及早就寢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然就熄燈了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手機照一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會吵到周圍的人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像只有我們四個人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們在海上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香  噓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香  你剛才想拿什麼出來?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水氣球？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在找泳衣的時候發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前大家一起玩過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩過玩過  凜子是最擅長充水的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了島上大家一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩  玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要玩  那就在找幾個那裏的小孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  暈船了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找個塑料袋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫乘務員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把船停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使停下來也是在海上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向神石許願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病也能治好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暈船不是病  說不定能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在這太平洋上許願？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英語作業做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天輪到我上去講
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香  凜  夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好上好  夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶字典了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:18:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一會兒再說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過一會兒借給我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天放晴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是大海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才發現？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為之前一直都漆黑一片的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個島？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不想去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  你從下田出來的時候起就一直讓人感覺很消沉似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有消沉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:20:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在想  這次是旅行  而下次再來就是搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不搬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就紗季一個人留下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使就到上完初中為止也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以來我家住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去那個島上的醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸以前就說想在那個島上工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個願望終於要達成了  所以非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人留下的話  這樣太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是沒辦法的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了  又說沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季一直都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要自欺欺人  要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說沒辦法  然後就放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季說不出口的話  我去說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去之後我去對叔叔說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他不要把紗季帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  因為  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  不能吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  我們沒吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你在哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.09,0:23:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候換的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.81,0:23:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.20,0:23:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有做準備運動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  你是這個島上的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你救了我朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你們這群外地人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.66,0:23:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什麼嘛  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.44,0:23:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  算什麼嘛  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味  島上的壽司超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.94,0:24:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季要搬到這種地方來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這島真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.98,0:24:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 夏色奇跡 第九話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.47,0:24:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途的天空的盡頭的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季去哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
